title: Dakine Over Under Travel Bag
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Over Under Travel Bag in our Northwest print.
Over Under Features:
- Expandable compartment
- Split level design allows for easy access
- Legal carry on size for most airlines (when not expanded)
- Exterior organizer pockets
- Retractable handle
- Replaceable urethane wheels
